The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                               Good Morning
      Hello It's Monday , February 25 , 2008                      
	Roads to     
	avoid    Brace Bridge, along Taratala Road, Sahapur, Tollygunge Circular Road and Prince Anwar Shah Road, between 8am and noon, for Madhyamik examinations. Traffic restrictions will be in force.     
	Games    The Telegraph Cup for corporates 2008 at CC amp;FC, 5pm.     
	Visit    Mohinder Amarnath to visit special school Nivedita Centre for Challenged Children, 10am.    
	Fair    Furniture, Kitchen and Lifestyle Fair at Ice Skating Rink, 11am to 8pm.    
	Music    An evening of classical music, featuring Pandit Asit Kumar Banerjee and Begum Shipra Khan, at EzCC, 6pm.     Programme of Geetanjali Music School at Rabindra Sadan, 5.30pm.    
	Art watch    In the Abyss, paintings by Manoj Kachangal, at Mon Art Gallerie, 11.30 am to 7pm.    Windows on the World, a solo show of paintings by Ranadip Mukherjee, at The Bengal Club, 4pm to 8pm.    Art works by Anju Chaudhuri at Gallery Sanskriti, 11am to 8pm.                                                                                                                                                                
